jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190107030602cUTXuin1KDJQZMOB.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190107030603EuSm1QpUH08ivzxa.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201901070306034qg1sJKC5xL8ihI9.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190107030601D7sO5z9KEPo1mnfW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190107030601YG9mBbz54OL8y7Ef.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong><a href=\"https://www.londonfashionweekmens.co.uk/Schedule#date07\" rel=\"nofollow\">伦敦男装周&nbsp;2019 秋冬于 1 月 5 日至 1 月 7 日举行。</a></strong></p><p>本次男装周共有 5 个中国设计师品牌参加：Pronounce、Private Policy（《智族》中国赞助）、Xander Zhou、Danshan、Feng Chen Wang。&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Pronounce 2019 秋冬：</strong></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190107014130eVOoAbp5air7RINu.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190107014131GczUS2ZnYXlwR7L4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190107014134JeLWhubUgZFv26yo.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190107014136MjFCG9mEcJq51Ugz.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20190107014141YgX73vLRHPueAmoD.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2019010701414249gtP5bN6GeyjOai.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"marg